Shoot.

108
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,640
Don't touch them!

109
00:04:40,850 --> 00:04:43,100
Back away from the Zs! It's not safe!

110
00:04:48,210 --> 00:04:49,090
No!

111
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:50,690
Don't touch them!

112
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:52,120
