117
00:05:05,910 --> 00:05:06,860
There you go.

118
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:16,720
This is gonna be one of them days, ain't it?

119
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:42,010
If you don't mind my asking,

120
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:45,110
