217
00:09:32,650 --> 00:09:33,630
Use whatever you have

218
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:36,180
to keep the Zs from getting too close.

219
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,860
They're very contaminated.

220
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:41,630
One hug and you'll be dead in a few hours.

221
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:44,590
Don't hug the zombies.

222
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,150
Got it.

223
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:47,710
You two stay here.

224
00:09:47,710 --> 00:09:49,580
10K, you cover us from up there.

225
00:09:49,580 --> 00:09:52,750
If we don't get back, you get him to California somehow.

226
00:09:53,350 --> 00:09:55,320
Come kid, you ready?

227
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,390
Let's do this.

228
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,650
10k!

229
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:01,620
Two thousand, three hundred and four.

230
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,860
Remember two minutes! No more!

231
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,440
Go!

232
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,730
Come on!

233
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:56,290
You got one more minute!

