00:11:09,330 --> 00:11:10,580
No hugging!

235
00:11:15,010 --> 00:11:16,280
Come on, let's go!

236
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,820
Time for you to go.

237
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,380
You got to go.

238
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:24,510
Go!

239
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,100
Heads up!

240
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,720
I got it.

