00:11:50,570 --> 00:11:51,710
Get out of here.

242
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,840
You're out of time.

243
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,800
You have to go. Go.

244
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:04,680
They're back.

245
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:12,550
I'm almost to the control room.

246
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:14,670
Great. Keep going, dad.

