00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:07,100
Dad. No! No!

265
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:09,030
No! Daddy.

266
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:11,340
No. Wake up. Please.

267
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:13,070
No!

268
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:15,770
No! No! No, no, please, no, not you dad!

269
00:13:15,770 --> 00:13:18,490
No! No! No!

270
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:21,170
No.

271
00:13:22,350 --> 00:13:23,340
Not you.

